law.text:
The Governor shall include in the budget bill for each fiscal year a General Fund appropriation for the following teacher retirement supplemental grants to the counties:
Allegany County - $1,632,106;
Baltimore City - $10,047,596;
Baltimore County - $3,000,000;
Caroline County - $685,108;
Dorchester County - $308,913;
Garrett County - $406,400;
Prince George's County - $9,628,702;
Somerset County - $381,999; and
Wicomico County - $1,567,837.
